		<h2>Welcome to DRAMP database!</h2>
        <hr />
		<p>DRAMP database is a manually curated data repository of antimicrobial peptides (AMPs), currently holding <strong>*** putative AMPs</strong> collected from public resource, <strong>*** clinical AMPs</strong> and <strong>*** patented AMPs</strong>. The peptides are less than 100 amino acids in length.<a id="more" href="home/read_more.html">Read More..</a>
</p>
